"\n"
"gdm: .su.dominio\n"

#: C/gdm.xml:1135(para)
msgid ""
"to your <filename>&lt;etc&gt;/hosts.allow</filename> if you normally "
"disallow all services from all hosts. See the <ulink type=\"help\" url=\"man:"
"hosts.allow\">hosts.allow(5)</ulink> man page for details."
msgstr ""
